35	/*
36	             ---------- <-
37	            |          |  \
38	          --| Program  |   \
39	         |  | 1 Header |   |
40	         |  |          |   |
41	         |   ----------    |
42	         |  |          |   |        ----------
43	       --|--| Program  |   |       |          |
44	      |  |  | 2 Header |   |       |ELF Header|
45	      |  |  |          |   \       |          |
46	      |  |   ----------     ------- ----------       ----> ----------
47	      |  |  |**********|           |          |     |     |          |
48	      |  |  |**********|           |          |     |     | Thread 1 |
49	      |  |  |**********|           |  Program |     |     | Registers|
50	      |  |  |**********|           |  Headers |     |     |          |
51	      |  |  |**********|           |          |     |      ----------
52	      |  |  |**********|           |          |    /      |          |
53	      |  |  |**********|           |          |   /       | Thread 2 |
54	      |  |   ----------            |          |  /        | Registers|
55	      |  |  |          |     ------ ---------- --         |          |
56	    --|--|--| Program  |    /      |          |            ----------
57	   |  |  |  | N Header |   |     ->|  Segment |           |**********|
58	   |  |  |  |          |   /    |  | (PT_NOTE)|           |**********|
59	   |  |  |   ---------- <--   --   |          |           |**********|
60	   |  |  |                   |      ---------- --         |**********|
61	   |  |   -------------------      |          |  \         ----------
62	   |  |                            |  Segment |   \       |          |
63	   |   --------------------------->| (PT_LOAD)|    |      | Thread N |
64	   |                               |          |    |      | Registers|
65	   |                                ----------     |      |          |
66	   |                               |          |    |       ----------
67	   |                               |  Segment |    \      |          |
68	   |                               | (PT_LOAD)|     \     |   AUXV   |
69	   |                               |          |      \    |          |
70	   |                                ----------        ---> ----------
71	   |                               |**********|
72	   |                               |**********|
73	   |                               |**********|
74	   |                               |**********|
75	   |                               |**********|
76	   |                                ----------
77	   |                               |          |
78	    ------------------------------>|  Segment |
79	                                   | (PT_LOAD)|
80	                                   |          |
81	                                    ----------
82	*/
